12.01	Raise_High_the_Roof_Beam,_Carpenters	Raise High the Roof Beam, Carpenters and Seymour: An Introduction	Raise High the Roof Beam, Carpenters and Seymour: An Introduction is a single volume featuring two novellas by J. D. Salinger, which were previously published in The New Yorker: Raise High the Roof Beam, Carpenters (1955) and Seymour: An Introduction (1959). Little, Brown republished them in this anthology in the year 1963. It was the first time the novellas had appeared in book form. Anthologized together, they were the third bestselling novel in the United States in 1963 according to Publishers Weekly.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/2/22/Seymoreintroduction.jpg/200px-Seymoreintroduction.jpg
